des:
This skill is a part of Mini Games.

Compare your answers against other players in hundreds of silly questions that you may struggle to decide an answer for.
All questions have yes or no answers.

For Example: You can have a personal butler, but they only serve you food using a slingshot. Yes or No?

It's Decision Time!

This skill is supported on all Alexa enabled devices, and has awesome visuals and animations for devices with screens, as well as hilarious sound effects!

If you launch this skill, it will tell you to open Mini Games.
